{"tid":758072,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"網民熱話：肉食者該死？素食偏激言論惹回響","createTime":"2018-07-27T10:52:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-27T12:59:50.000Z","uid":153228,"like":2,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"4fe900665b85880ad08962be6cd58579bbddd0b1","tid":758072,"uid":153228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T10:52:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180727/bkn-20180727181413168-0727_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180727%2Fbkn-20180727181413168-0727_00822_001.html&d=Vfy%2F7%2BqEJ3MUExm9UiD0ZU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=0e32b4e8\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180727/bkn-20180727181413168-0727_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180727/photo/bkn-20180727181413168-0727_00822_001_01p.jpg?20180727183652\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180727%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180727181413168-0727_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20180727183652&h=b9ad5410&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有自稱素食者指「希望肉食者盡快死晒」，言論引起極大回響。（健吾fb圖片）<br />\n<br />\n為健康、道德論、宗教理由等&hellip;&hellip;都是素食者選擇食素的原因，不少素食者亦會嘗試將理念推廣，說服更多人加入素食行列。但前日（25日）開始網上熱傳一張截圖，有自稱素食的網民留下偏激的言論「希望肉食者盡快死晒」，最後兩邊不討好，素食者、肉食者都一同聲討該網民。<br />\n<br />\n食肉、食素各有選擇，態度過於偏激，只會惹來反效果。作家「健吾」在其Facebook分享一張留言截圖，一名網民指香港對素食者不公平，表示希望肉食者死以平衡比例，認為是「畀番尊重不殺生的好人」。該網民又指與親朋戚友食飯十分難受，「佢哋一日唔死都唔會有人食飯會就自己」。<br />\n<br />\n其言論在網上引起極大回響，有人表示想得到別人尊重，先要尊重別人。有素食網民指其言論「影衰」一眾素食者，加深雙方誤解，是走火入魔。也有人指素食與否，只要互相包容即可，河水不犯井水亦毋須對立，甚至有人將留言者起底，質疑對方是「偽素食者」，故意挑起事端。<br />\n<br />\n網民有話說<br />\nLi Tsz Fung：叫肉食者死呢下已經係提倡殺生嘅行為啦<br />\n<br />\nRaymond Mok：其實植物一樣有生命...<br />\n<br />\nPing Yin Leung：肉食者好少迫害素食者，本身河水不犯井水，不過近排真係好多呢啲素膠攻擊post"},{"pid":"45d5fa2cf219531f98ce134fe61e815b3428510e","tid":758072,"uid":19978,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T10:56:03.000Z","msg":"佢痴左線啊佢"},{"pid":"7aac297c76de3e307052e8f56c44d51cd240baa0","tid":758072,"uid":141297,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T10:59:00.000Z","msg":"曲線？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f21871834cb144d1abc17f4317dbec9eb32cb930","tid":758072,"uid":14250,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T10:59:05.000Z","msg":"全香港有九成幾人要死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ffce2330544f7550ec9e95abfcee7521b4fa6e7","tid":758072,"uid":34517,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T11:00:43.000Z","msg":"素食者 女人 同性戀 變性人 回教徒 殘疾 精神病<br />\n<br />\n左膠仲有冇題材可以發揮？"},{"pid":"dc6e9bd69a19f490fa37d5f34a4b7ac897ba26c4","tid":758072,"uid":55458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T11:00:52.000Z","msg":"食素食者肉"},{"pid":"3a7e23b39739bfae5d8911e727bbe344d6dc1964","tid":758072,"uid":11694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T11:01:14.000Z","msg":"佢九成半路先轉食齋，咁佢應唔應該死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8196f1ce1bc1826f8c06c20881ce06699bf8e74","tid":758072,"uid":40381,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T11:03:17.000Z","msg":"其實食素好唔cost effective"},{"pid":"a535176a6879e28f5ccd96ee6f599ddf21f0e754","tid":758072,"uid":175108,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T11:04:11.000Z","msg":"棵菜唔識郁唔識叫代表佢冇生命可以任你食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要黎種農作物嘅耕地唔係開墾荒野所得，耕田呢個過程唔會有任何動物受害<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你話宗教問題，口味問題我完全接受<br />\n但講到唔想殺生咁偉大就唔該係屋企露台種果實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88042883d5ed1040ba69704950bb24bbad925eb1","tid":758072,"uid":10340,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T11:04:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/HgKflIc_d.jpg?maxwidth=640&amp;shape=thumb&amp;fidelity=high\" dat